    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Epiphany City》是一款可爱的“n”创意益智冒险游戏，你可以使用神奇的画框以烧脑的方式来操纵你周围的世界。让绘画成真，改变时间，重新想象物体来满足你的需要。跟着 Lily，一个失去了所有希望的女孩，从最强大的超级英雄那里偷走了力量，以此承担拯救世界的任务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>重新构造物品</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们独特的拼图机制将让你以富有想象力的全新方式看待世界。看起来像一件东西的物体可以变成完全不同的东西，这取决于它们周围的环境。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1508530/extras/032f125c061dad8f443730d539789921.poster.avif?t=1753911195\" width=500 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1508530/extras/032f125c061dad8f443730d539789921.webm?t=1753911195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1508530/extras/032f125c061dad8f443730d539789921.mp4?t=1753911195\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>操纵世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lily 的神奇画框力量随着你的前进而强大，让你能以越来越多的方式改变世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1508530/extras/2ecc4c6b0b728e6bf32f2a6a291454c7.poster.avif?t=1753911195\" width=500 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1508530/extras/2ecc4c6b0b728e6bf32f2a6a291454c7.webm?t=1753911195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1508530/extras/2ecc4c6b0b728e6bf32f2a6a291454c7.mp4?t=1753911195\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>实现预言</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >帮助 Lily，因为她试图通过实现一个神之预言来拯救世界……即使这本不是她的宿命。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1508530/extras/be4defa5a07247e5e57ec9d48ce3fa8d.poster.avif?t=1753911195\" width=500 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1508530/extras/be4defa5a07247e5e57ec9d48ce3fa8d.webm?t=1753911195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1508530/extras/be4defa5a07247e5e57ec9d48ce3fa8d.mp4?t=1753911195\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>寻找希望，即使你一无所有</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这个场景并不能真正帮上忙……但结局会！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1508530/extras/fd0ce29778575d4a24af967222d977fd.poster.avif?t=1753911195\" width=500 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1508530/extras/fd0ce29778575d4a24af967222d977fd.webm?t=1753911195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1508530/extras/fd0ce29778575d4a24af967222d977fd.mp4?t=1753911195\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>特点</strong></u></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 独特的拼图机制强调要跳出思维束腹，不仅仅是标准的“推块”或“锁&amp;键”类型</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 多样化和富有表现力的角色，你一定会爱上——超过 1000 个独特的手绘人物头像和精灵</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 《Epiphany City》讲述了一个傻傻的、异想天开的，但同时又非常燃的故事，它反对社会上让人喘不过气的种种想法，反对绝望和妄自菲薄的感觉</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 精炼的教程和简单的控制确保你不浪费时间又能获得乐趣。非常适合与想要开始玩游戏的家庭成员或其他重要的人一起体验！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 《Epiphany City》是一款可玩性高、令人陶醉和充满惊讶的游戏，容易上手，也能带来充满惊喜的烧脑之旅！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1508530/extras/599b71c5458abc23d40af9e59f0af8eb.avif?t=1753911195\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p>",
